{"tid":1173645,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭學生舉報發表「損害國家聲譽」言論　重慶師大教授被貶圖書館工作","createTime":"2019-05-27T09:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T09:56:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"79221bfd9360e72f015e7e2c012633f259941fc4","tid":1173645,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/teacher-08_4M84z_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fteacher-08_4M84z_1200x0.png&h=3249025f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年 2 月被學生舉報在課堂上「發表損害國家聲譽言論」的重慶師範大學副教授唐雲，微博傳出校方最近發出的「人事調動通知」顯示，他在今個月開始被調往學校圖書館「從事其他專業技術崗工作」。<br />\n<br />\n將於下月踏入 56 歲的唐雲，1986 年開始在重慶師範大學任教，自 1997 年起已擔任副教授。重慶範大學的紅頭文件顯示，指唐雲在在今年 2 月 25日在「魯迅研究」課程中，「發表損害國家聲譽的言論」，遭學生舉報。文件指他「違反政治紀律，嚴重違反教師職業道德，在師生造成了不良影響。」他早前已被撤銷教師資格，並予以降級處分，由專業技術五級降至七級。<br />\n<br />\n微博傳出校方最近發出的「人事調動通知」顯示，唐雲由本月20日調往學校圖書館「從事其他專業技術崗工作」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E59490E99BB2_O78Ms_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE59490E99BB2_O78Ms_1200x0.jpg&h=f28b07ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他今年三月在微信寫的一首新詩《告別》，回應自己被降級處分：「這是我的講台；三十三年後我第一次離開，這是我的學生，他們並不都是猶大。今天披著恥辱離去；明天，我定會戴著桂冠而來，這是我的講台。」並附上大學課室及監獄的照片。<br />\n<br />\n唐雲是重慶南川人，1986年四川師範大學畢業後，到重慶師範大學工作 33 年。唐雲是該校校歌的填詞人。<br />\n<br />\n唐雲因在《魯迅研究》課程教學中，發表損害國家聲譽的言論，違反政治紀律和教師職業道德，對師生造成不良影響，大學校長辦公會研究後決定，報請重慶市教委，撤銷他的教師資格，但文件無透露唐雲，到底在課堂說了甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/遭學生舉報發表-損害國家聲譽-言論-重慶師大教授被貶圖書館工作/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E9%81%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%88%89%E5%A0%B1%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8-%E6%90%8D%E5%AE%B3%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E8%81%B2%E8%AD%BD-%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96-%E9%87%8D%E6%85%B6%E5%B8%AB%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88%E8%A2%AB%E8%B2%B6%E5%9C%96%E6%9B%B8%E9%A4%A8%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%2F&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWBBk8ry%2Bv12G5j1RUyKX8i0%3D&h=e36c5972\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E9%81%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%88%89%E5%A0%B1%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8-%E6%90%8D%E5%AE%B3%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E8%81%B2%E8%AD%BD-%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96-%E9%87%8D%E6%85%B6%E5%B8%AB%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88%E8%A2%AB%E8%B2%B6%E5%9C%96%E6%9B%B8%E9%A4%A8%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%2F&h=2a9e21ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/遭學生舉報發表-損害國家聲譽-言論-重慶師大教授被貶圖書館工作/</a>"},{"pid":"c250f38fc987e1e0b8c4c202527914afbeb06d3d","tid":1173645,"uid":192581,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:18:59.000Z","msg":"批鬥革命仍續 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b08c246280aea04b9b46487fd96ba907ad0d73","tid":1173645,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:28:19.000Z","msg":"破四舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3248d7f791919422f863a64f7c0b16c38906857","tid":1173645,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:29:12.000Z","msg":"文革再臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140cf8489d34260eb685ee41462be42f8cd2dabc","tid":1173645,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:39:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mC2WaEpyunA&amp;t=462s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmC2WaEpyunA%26t%3D462s&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWBBk8ry%2Bv12G5j1RUyKX8i0%3D&h=32a0ab9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mC2WaEpyunA&amp;t=462s</a>"},{"pid":"24397f2b44f484119c5658416fa5a53a3ce0e71d","tid":1173645,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:44:01.000Z","msg":"生而為支鬼 我很抱歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9993bd394a423c9befd6d1e1